alification competition after the ordeal she has undergone to get to her third Olympics 16 years after her first.\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2702, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Downie\", \"from\": 2530, \"to\": 2536}, {\"ngram\": \"the arena\", \"from\": 2563, \"to\": 2572}, {\"ngram\": \"the first qualification competition\", \"from\": 2577, \"to\": 2612}, {\"ngram\": \"the ordeal\", \"from\": 2619, \"to\": 2629}, {\"ngram\": \"her third Olympics\", \"from\": 2658, \"to\": 2676}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her brother died suddenly of an undiagnosed heart condition just before the Olympic trials for Tokyo.\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2805, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2799, \"end\": 2804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9999994514111362, \"rank\": 5.361561716518169e-07, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her brother\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2715}, {\"ngram\": \"an undiagnosed heart condition\", \"from\": 2733, \"to\": 2763}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic trials\", \"from\": 2776, \"to\": 2794}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And she was one of the most senior gymnasts to speak out in the abuse row that overshadowed the sport in Britain.\", \"from\": 2806, \"to\": 2919, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2911, \"end\": 2918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9807241247406269, \"rank\": 0.019654384339359884, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most senior gymnasts\", \"from\": 2825, \"to\": 2849}, {\"ngram\": \"the abuse row\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2879}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2898, \"to\": 2907}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She revealed weight shaming leading to injuries and ins